{"tid":762133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=馬戲？2地盤工危坐14米高天秤追薪","createTime":"2018-07-31T04:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T13:11:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"768686e20ee8775b43226ba2f26127bc11c7b431","tid":762133,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:23:20.000Z","msg":"赤鱲角航展道近博覽館一個建築地盤，今早(31日)9時01分，兩名工人聲稱被拖欠薪金，分別爬上2號及3號、逾<span style=\"color: red;\">14米高天秤上危坐</span>，向資方追討欠薪，其他工人見狀報警。消防接報到場，在地面張開救生氣墊戒備，警方亦召來談判專家到場展開游說，雙方目前仍在對峙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180731/photo/bkn-20180731100248163-0731_00822_001_02b.jpg?20180731121121\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180731%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180731100248163-0731_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20180731121121&h=54a5835d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180731/bkn-20180731100248163-0731_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180731%2Fbkn-20180731100248163-0731_00822_001.html&d=IuKNOLbpE%2FhetUGzojZuLQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=1cb9bdab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180731/bkn-20180731100248163-0731_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9c3faf4d8e6200814f9241e6c518727720a093e0","tid":762133,"uid":17738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:43:48.000Z","msg":"佬綜。。。。贏家.jpg"},{"pid":"6be3fe598038001b036932c4b7eef72e5f433fb1","tid":762133,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c3faf4d8e6200814f9241e6c518727720a093e0","tid":762133,"uid":17738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:43:48.000Z","msg":"佬綜。。。。贏家.jpg"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:44:49.000Z","msg":"資方A.gif"},{"pid":"c5484558a44860a10abe0266b3150d28de6b61c9","tid":762133,"uid":13303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04